<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>北陸古韻之旅 🏯 7天6夜親子行程</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500;700;900&family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        :root {
            --primary-red: #8B2500;
            --secondary-gold: #D4A574;
            --bamboo-green: #5F7161;
            --paper-beige: #F4EFE6;
            --ink-black: #2C2416;
            --tea-brown: #6B5B3C;
            --sakura-pink: #E8B4BC;
            --temple-grey: #6B6B6B;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #F4EFE6 0%, #E8DCC8 100%);
            color: var(--ink-black);
            line-height: 1.8;
            position: relative;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* 紙紋理背景 */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: 
                repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 2px, rgba(139, 37, 0, 0.02) 2px, rgba(139, 37, 0, 0.02) 4px);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* 頁首 */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border: 3px solid var(--primary-red);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            position: relative;
        }

        header::before,
        header::after {
            content: '◆';
            position: absolute;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--primary-red);
        }

        header::before {
            top: 10px;
            left: 20px;
        }

        header::after {
            bottom: 10px;
            right: 20px;
        }

        .main-title {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-red);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 0px rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.5);
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            color: var(--bamboo-green);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .travel-info {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--tea-brown);
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .family-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--sakura-pink);
            color: var(--primary-red);
            padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 2px solid var(--primary-red);
        }

        /* 總覽區 */
        .overview {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            border: 2px solid var(--secondary-gold);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .overview-title {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--primary-red);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-bottom: 3px solid var(--secondary-gold);
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        .info-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(244, 239, 230, 0.8), rgba(232, 220, 200, 0.8));
            border: 2px solid var(--bamboo-green);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .info-box:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        .info-box h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--primary-red);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .info-box p {
            color: var(--ink-black);
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        /* Day 卡片 */
        .day-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            border: 3px solid var(--primary-red);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            position: relative;
        }

        .day-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -3px;
            left: -3px;
            right: -3px;
            bottom: -3px;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary-red), var(--secondary-gold));
            border-radius: 15px;
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .day-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: -15px;
            left: 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-red), #B8341F);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(139, 37, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .day-header {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .day-title {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--primary-red);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .day-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--bamboo-green);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* 展開收縮按鈕 */
        .collapse-toggle {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bamboo-green), #7A8A75);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(95, 113, 97, 0.4);
            width: 100%;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
        }

        .collapse-toggle:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F5F51, #5F7161);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(95, 113, 97, 0.5);
        }

        .collapse-toggle .arrow {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .collapse-toggle.expanded .arrow {
            transform: rotate(180deg);
        }

        .activities-container {
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: max-height 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        .activities-container.expanded {
            max-height: 5000px;
            transition: max-height 0.8s ease-in;
        }

        /* 活動列表 */
        .activities {
            list-style: none;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        .activity {
            background: rgba(244, 239, 230, 0.6);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary-gold);
            border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            margin: 1rem 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .activity:hover {
            background: rgba(232, 180, 188, 0.2);
            border-left-color: var(--primary-red);
            transform: translateX(8px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .activity-time {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--bamboo-green);
            color: white;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
        }

        .activity-name {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--ink-black);
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .activity-duration {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(212, 165, 116, 0.3);
            color: var(--tea-brown);
            padding: 0.2rem 0.7rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-left: 0.5rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-gold);
            font-weight: 600;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
        }

        .activity-note {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--bamboo-green);
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
            padding-left: 1rem;
            border-left: 2px solid var(--bamboo-green);
            font-style: italic;
        }

        /* 住宿 */
        .accommodation {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(232, 180, 188, 0.3), rgba(232, 180, 188, 0.5));
            border: 2px solid var(--sakura-pink);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .accommodation::before {
            content: '🏯';
            font-size: 1.8rem;
        }

        .accommodation-text {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--primary-red);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* 裝飾分隔線 */
        .divider {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 3rem 0;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--primary-red);
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        /* 頁尾 */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 0;
            margin-top: 4rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            border-radius: 15px;
            border-top: 3px solid var(--primary-red);
        }

        .footer-text {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--ink-black);
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* 響應式 */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .main-title {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            .info-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .day-title {
                font-size: 1.4rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="main-title">北陸古韻之旅</div>
            <div class="subtitle">🏯 探訪古城 · 品味歷史 · 親子同遊 🏯</div>
            <div class="travel-info">2026年9月24日 - 9月30日</div>
            <div class="family-tag">👨‍👩‍👧 親子旅行 · 2大1小</div>
        </header>

        <!-- 旅程總覽 -->
        <div class="overview">
            <h2 class="overview-title">旅程總覽</h2>
            
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-box">
                    <h3>✈️ 去程航班</h3>
                    <p>
                        2026年9月24日 (四)<br>
                        桃園機場 → 中部國際機場<br>
                        國泰航空 CX530<br>
                        11:30 → 15:30
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <h3>✈️ 回程航班</h3>
                    <p>
                        2026年9月30日 (三)<br>
                        小松機場 → 桃園機場<br>
                        長榮航空 BR157<br>
                        11:45 → 13:55
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <h3>🚗 交通方式</h3>
                    <p>
                        9/24: 地鐵 & JR<br>
                        9/25-9/27: 租車自駕<br>
                        NIPPON RENT A CAR<br>
                        米原店取車 → 金澤西口站還車<br>
                        9/28-9/30: 地鐵 & 公車
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <h3>🏨 住宿安排</h3>
                    <p>
                        9/24: 東橫INN 米原西口站<br>
                        9/25: Route Inn Takefu Inter<br>
                        9/26: コンフォートイン福井<br>
                        9/27-9/29: 微笑飯店金澤駅前東口 (3晚)
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="divider">◈ ◈ ◈</div>

        <!-- Day 1 -->
        <div class="day-card">
            <div class="day-badge">第1天 🌸</div>
            <div class="day-header">
                <h2 class="day-title">DAY 1</h2>
                <p class="day-subtitle">2026年9月24日 (四) - 啟程前往北陸</p>
            </div>
            
            <button class="collapse-toggle" onclick="toggleDay(this)">
                <span>展開行程</span>
                <span class="arrow">▼</span>
            </button>

            <div class="activities-container">
                <ul class="activities">
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">11:30 出發</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">桃園機場出發</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">15:30 抵達</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">抵達中部國際機場</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">16:00 - 16:30</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            機場4F えびせんべいの里買蝦餅
                            <span class="activity-duration">30分鐘</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-note">名古屋名產，多種口味蝦餅試吃選購</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">16:45 - 18:00</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            矢場丼豬排機場店吃晚餐
                            <span class="activity-duration">1小時15分</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-note">名古屋必吃味噌豬排飯</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">18:15 - 18:45</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            搭乘μ-sky往名鐵名古屋
                            <span class="activity-duration">30分鐘</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">19:00 - 19:45</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            轉乘JR名古屋往米原
                            <span class="activity-duration">45分鐘</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">20:00 入住</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">東橫INN 米原西口站 CHECK IN</div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="accommodation">
                    <span class="accommodation-text">住宿：東橫INN 米原西口站</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Day 2 -->
        <div class="day-card">
            <div class="day-badge">第2天 🏯</div>
            <div class="day-header">
                <h2 class="day-title">DAY 2</h2>
                <p class="day-subtitle">2026年9月25日 (五) - 彥根城探訪 · 黑壁廣場</p>
            </div>
            
            <button class="collapse-toggle" onclick="toggleDay(this)">
                <span>展開行程</span>
                <span class="arrow">▼</span>
            </button>

            <div class="activities-container">
                <ul class="activities">
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">08:00 - 09:00</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            飯店享用早餐
                            <span class="activity-duration">1小時</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">09:00 取車</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">NIPPON RENT A CAR 米原店租車</div>
                        <div class="activity-note">開始3天自駕之旅</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">09:30 - 12:00</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            彥根城參觀
                            <span class="activity-duration">2.5小時</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-note">日本國寶天守閣之一，欣賞琵琶湖美景</div>
                        <div class="activity-note">參觀彥根城博物館，觀賞彥根喵表演</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">12:30 - 13:45</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            比内地鶏夢京橋店午餐
                            <span class="activity-duration">1小時15分</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-note">品嚐秋田比內地雞料理</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">14:00 - 14:30</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            前往長濱市
                            <span class="activity-duration">30分鐘車程</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">14:30 - 17:30</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            長濱市黑壁廣場漫步
                            <span class="activity-duration">3小時</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-note">江戶時代街道，參觀黑壁玻璃館</div>
                        <div class="activity-note">逛特色小店，品嚐當地點心</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">18:00 - 18:30</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            前往武生
                            <span class="activity-duration">30分鐘車程</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">18:30 入住</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">Route Inn Takefu Inter Hotel CHECK IN</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">19:00 - 20:15</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            COCO一番屋武生店晚餐
                            <span class="activity-duration">1小時15分</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-note">日式咖哩專賣店，適合親子用餐</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">20:30 - 21:15</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            Seria 武生楽市店採購物品
                            <span class="activity-duration">45分鐘</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-note">百元商店採購旅行用品</div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="accommodation">
                    <span class="accommodation-text">住宿：Route Inn Takefu Inter Hotel</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Day 3 -->
        <div class="day-card">
            <div class="day-badge">第3天 🦕</div>
            <div class="day-header">
                <h2 class="day-title">DAY 3</h2>
                <p class="day-subtitle">2026年9月26日 (六) - 越前大野城 · 恐龍博物館</p>
            </div>
            
            <button class="collapse-toggle" onclick="toggleDay(this)">
                <span>展開行程</span>
                <span class="arrow">▼</span>
            </button>

            <div class="activities-container">
                <ul class="activities">
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">07:30 - 08:30</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            飯店享用早餐
                            <span class="activity-duration">1小時</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">08:30 - 09:00</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            前往四季の餅 あめこ
                            <span class="activity-duration">30分鐘車程</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">09:00 - 09:30</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            四季の餅 あめこ購買伴手禮
                            <span class="activity-duration">30分鐘</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-note">當地知名麻糬店</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">09:30 - 10:20</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            前往越前大野城
                            <span class="activity-duration">50分鐘車程</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">10:20 - 12:00</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            越前大野城參觀
                            <span class="activity-duration">1小時40分</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-note">天空之城，登城眺望大野市街</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">12:15 - 13:30</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            そば処 福そば午餐
                            <span class="activity-duration">1小時15分</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-note">品嚐正宗越前蕎麥麵</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">13:45 - 14:15</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            伊藤順和堂購買伴手禮
                            <span class="activity-duration">30分鐘</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-note">羽二重餅等福井名產</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">14:30 - 15:30</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            福井恐龍博物館外觀拍照
                            <span class="activity-duration">1小時</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="activity-note">世界三大恐龍博物館之一，外觀拍照留念</div>
                        <div class="activity-note">若時間充裕可考慮入館參觀（需另購票）</div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">16:00 - 16:30</div>
                        <div class="activity-name">
                            前往福井市區
                            <span class="activity-duration">30分鐘車程</span>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="activity">
                        <div class="activity-time">16:30 入住</div>
